ies</span></li></ol></ol></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 108pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 64.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">The research will report on issues </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">including</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> children accessing inappropriate adult content as well as</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> managing abusive and threatening behaviours</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 64.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">The outcome will be disseminated in the form of key recommendations relevant to the development of safety awareness and policy </span><a name="_ftnref4"></a><a href="#_ftn4">[4]</a></li></ul></ul><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 72pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">We </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">welcome the opportunity to discuss </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">our findings </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">with the C</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">MS Select C</span><span style="fon